$interpreted: ? ? ?: Vanessa.
Bandit Leader: Man, waiting for that golem to fall asleep almost had us falling asleep.
Vanessa: Why are you here?
Bandit Leader: My men wanted to make their move that day. You stopped them, saying that we should wait for the gem rocks on his back to grow.
Bandit Leader: But we need the cash now. We can't wait anymore.
Vanessa: Hold on, it's not worth it... How about we...
Bandit Leader: ...You trying to buy it time or something? You fallin' in love with it or something?
Bandit Leader: I gotta remind you of all the rare creatures you sold us before? Where'd that conscience come from all the sudden?
Vanessa: If it weren't for Walt, I would never have been a part of this...
Bandit Leader: Oh yeah, your son's still getting treatment, right? Well then I guess it'd be a shame to run out of money, huh?
Golemwalt: Grrrooouuu~
Bandit Leader: Damn, already awake. Everybody, prepare yourselves!
Vanessa: No, please don't hurt Golemwalt. He saved my life... I-I'll find a more valuable creature to sell you!
Bandit Leader: Shut it!
Golemwalt: Grrrooouuu!!
Vanessa: Golemwalt, forget about me. RUN!
Bandit Leader: Dammit, no one's getting away!
Vanessa: Bears!?
Golemwalt: Grrrooouuu!
Razorclaw: Calm down. Crushfang is just checking for injuries.
Crushfang: No big deal, just small scratches. A quick patching should do the job.
Golemwalt: Grrrouuu~
Vanessa: Haha, stop it, Golemwalt~
Crushfang: You gave the golem a name?
Razorclaw: This human doesn't look like a bad person. She took a blow for this golem, too... I say we let her go.
Crushfang: Fine. But the golem comes back to Totemtaff with us.
Golemwalt: Grrrooouuu!
Vanessa: Golemwalt, being away from home is dangerous. You should go back.
Golemwalt: Grrrouuu...
Vanessa: Take care, Golemwalt.
Golemwalt: Grrrouuu...
Vanessa: Stop following me, go with them!
Vanessa: I have a sick son back home to worry about. I can't take care of you anymore!
Vanessa: Golemwalt! What are you doing?
Vanessa: Is this... for me?
Crushfang: What's this golem doing? Giving the human a gem rock? Come on, all they'll do is sell it!
Vanessa: These are worth money? Golemwalt... you knew I needed money? For my son?
Golemwalt: Grrrouuu...
Vanessa: Thank you, Golemwalt. Thank you so much...
Crushfang: Razorclaw, what do we do?
Razorclaw: It's just a small piece, forget it.
Vanessa: Golemwalt, I really have to go now. Goodbye. I hope to see you again someday.
